Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: skitter facts
des:
Skitter Facts tells you interesting and true facts about Skitter, the protagonist of the web serial Worm.

To Enable the Skill: Say "Alexa, enable Skitter Facts" or search for "Skitter Facts" in the Alexa mobile app or at Amazon.com. Click the enable button on the Skitter Facts skill page.

To Get Started: Say "Alexa ask Skitter Facts for a fact". Enjoy your true fact.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
